data.description: WELCOME TO LEISURE VILLAGE, AN ACTIVE 55+ GATED COMMUNITY IN THE HEART OF THE CHAIN O'LAKES AREA. THIS NICELY UPDATED TWO BEDROOM HOME WITH 4 SEASON SUN ROOM AND EXTRA DEEP GARAGE OFFERS A NICE AMOUNT OF SPACE... OVER 1000 SQ FT AND LOWER HOA FEES OF ONLY $277 PER MONTH... FOR ALL THIS PRIVATE COMMUNITY OFFERS! DUPLEX STYLE UNIT OFFERS NEWER EXTERIOR DOORS AND STORM DOORS AND ALL NEWER WIDOWS THROUGHOUT INSTALLED APPROX 5 YEARS AGO. NEW LVP FLOORING INSTALLED AUGUST 2023. THE EAT IN KITCHEN BOASTS NEWER GRANITE COUNTERS AND TILE FLOOR AND ALL APPLIANCES STAY INCLUDING MICROWAVE. SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM OFFERS SPACE FOR A DINING AREA AND FEATURES NEW LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORING. FOUR SEASON SUN ROOM ALSO FEATURES LAMINATE FLOOR AND DOOR TO PATIO AND WALKING PATH. SPACIOUS MASTER BEDROOM AND SECOND BEDROOM WITH EXTRA TALL CLOSET DOORS FOR EASY ACCESS TO UPPER SHELVING AND FRESHLY STEAM CLEANED CARPETS IN SEPTEMBER 2023. BEAUTIFUL NEW WALK-IN SHOWER INSTALLED FEBRUARY 2023 AND NEW TOILET IN 2022. ALL WALLS, CEILINGS & TRIM FRESHLY PAINTED 12/23. LARGE WASHER AND DRYER IN LAUNDRY CLOSET WITH WATER SOFTENER AND AIR HANDLER. NEW WATER HEATER AUGUST 2023. ALL WINDOW SILLS, GARAGE FLOOR PAINTED AND MOTIONS SENSOR LIGHT IN GARAGE INSTALLED AUGUST 2023. NEW CENTRAL AIR UNIT INSTALLED IN LAST 5 YEARS. LEISURE VILLAGE RESIDENTS ENJOY AN AMAZING 100 ACRE PARK-LIKE AND RESORT STYLE SETTING OFFERING A BEAUTIFUL PRIVATE LAKE WITH LAKEFRONT PICNIC AREAS AND FIRE PIT, PAR-3, 9-HOLE GOLF COURSE, LARGE RECREATION CENTER WITH LOBBY FEATURING ATRIUM AREA WITH TABLE AND CHAIRS FOR RESIDENTS TO GATHER AND SITTING AREA WITH TV, LEISURE HALL AUDITORIUM IS PERFECT FOR COMMUNITY THEME PARTIES OR PRIVATE GATHERINGS, FITNESS ROOM, LIBRARY WITH A VARIETY OF BOOKS PLUS AUDIO/VIDEO LIBRARY AND COMPUTER, LOUNGE WITH TV AND SPACE FOR COMMITTEE MEETINGS, ART ROOM, WOOD WORKING ROOM, SEWING & QUILTING ROOM, GAME ROOM WITH POOL TABLES, PING PONG & POKER TABLES AND A MEETING/CONFERENCE ROOM. PRIVATE LEISURE LAKE IS STOCKED WITH FISH AND OFFERS 2 ROW BOATS, DOCK AND GAZEBO. TWO OTHER GAZEBOS ARE FOUND ON FRIENDSHIP LAKE (POND) AND AT THE REC CENTER. OTHER OUTDOOR AMENITIES OFFERED ARE GREENHOUSE WITH GARDEN PLOTS, TENNIS OR PICKLE BALL COURTS, BOCCE BALL, SHUFFLEBOARD & HEATED POOL WITH LOUNGE CHAIRS, SHADY CABANAS AND UMBRELLA TABLES WITH CHAIRS. LEISURE VILLAGE ALSO FEATURES A 14 PASSENGER BUS THAT TAKES RESIDENTS TO COMMUNITY DINNER OUTINGS AND SHOPPING TRIPS. DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS FANTASTIC LISTING IN A FABULOUS PRIVATE 55+ COMMUNITY.
